OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with rain
OL,6,Fspreading east for a time. A few
OL,7,Fbright or sunny intervals this
OL,8,Fafternoon along with a few showers,
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy. Colder than of
OL,10,Flate.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will see
OL,13,Fscattered showers. Showers gradually
OL,14,Fdying out through the early hours,
OL,15,Fbecoming dry by dawn. A cold night
OL,16,Fwith frost in sheltered glens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
