OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,6,Fsunshine. Dry and cloudier in the
OL,7,Fafternoon, patchy rain spreading
OL,8,Fnortheast in the evening along with
OL,9,Fstrengthening southeasterly winds.
OL,10,FRather cold.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOvernight rain clearing away on
OL,14,FSaturday morning then mainly dry and
OL,15,Fbright with occasional showers. More
OL,16,Fin the way of showers on Sunday and
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
